  "detailed_description": "MemeNgin is a software that helps you to design the progress of meme creation.<br>You change the shape and color of images. add a text, and try some cool effects too.<br>then assemble multiple images into one, using compositing nodes.<br><strong>Sounds too complex?</strong> then you can just start from other templates from the workshop.<br>you can build awesome meme templates with minimal efforts!<br><br>MemeNgin is a opensource project. you can participate a project in any form, or check out what MemeNgin is about  in a github.",
  "about_the_game": "MemeNgin is a software that helps you to design the progress of meme creation.<br>You change the shape and color of images. add a text, and try some cool effects too.<br>then assemble multiple images into one, using compositing nodes.<br><strong>Sounds too complex?</strong> then you can just start from other templates from the workshop.<br>you can build awesome meme templates with minimal efforts!<br><br>MemeNgin is a opensource project. you can participate a project in any form, or check out what MemeNgin is about  in a github.",
